==English==

===Etymology===
From {{L.}} ''[[plumosus]]'', from ''[[pluma]]'' "feather": compare French ''[[plumeux]]''.

===Adjective===
'''plumose'''
# Having [[feather]]s or [[plume]]s.
# Having [[hair]]s, or other párts, arranged along an [[axis]] like a feather; [[feathery]]; [[plumelike]]; as, a plumose leaf; plumose tentacles.

